---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Notary Service Areas | Mobile Notary Across the Las Vegas Valley"
description: "Mobile notary coverage across the Las Vegas valley: Las Vegas, Henderson, North Las Vegas, Summerlin, Paradise, Spring Valley, Enterprise, Green Valley, Anthem, and beyond."
permalink: "/service-areas/"
---
{% block content %}
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <span>Service Areas</span></nav>
    <h1>Where We Go</h1>
    <p class="lede">Everywhere in the Las Vegas valley — and farther for loan signings and facility visits. Every quote includes the full travel fee upfront, so distance is never a surprise.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-gold" href="tel:{{ site.phoneHref }}">Call {{ site.phone }}</a>
      <a class="btn btn-navy" href="/#book">Request an appointment</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Featured areas</h2>
    <div class="card-grid">
      {%- for a in collections.areas %}
      <a class="card" href="{{ a.url }}"><h3>{{ a.data.short_title }}</h3><p>{{ a.data.lede }}</p></a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Also covered</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 44em; color: var(--slate);">Las Vegas proper (every neighborhood, downtown to the Strip), Sunrise Manor, Green Valley, Anthem, Centennial Hills, Aliante, Whitney, Winchester, Mountain's Edge, Southern Highlands, Boulder City, and out to the master-planned edges of the valley. Outside the valley? Ask — the answer is usually yes with a travel adjustment quoted before you commit to anything.</p>
  </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
